text: Food is ok but severely overpriced to the point where a lukewarm burger with the most basic fillings costs $8.50 to buy. One waffle smothered in plastic with no toppings will cost you $2.50. Overuse of non-disposable plastic wrapping in both cookies and waffles. Muffins are delicious however.
The Dover Court school cantine in all its breadth and inherent culinary impediments
